Fujian Zhangzhou issued new regulations on fishing boat control. The article emphasized that some fishermen will be controlled as incoming personnel, and "2+3" isolation will be implemented from the 19th, that is, 2 days of centralized isolation and 3 days of home isolation. 0+3 will be implemented from January 9, 2023.
However, the current national entry control policy is 5+3, and Zhangzhou's policy coincides with the dates of the entry 2+3 and 0+3 that were previously rumored to be implemented online, so it is very intriguing.
